commitResults.messageBody:
AddLessonCommand directly mutates the tutee rather than create a new
tutee from scratch. This causes test cases in EditCommand and
RemarkCommand to fail when AddLessonCommand is ran before them.

Let's fix this by creating a new tutee each time we run
AddLessonCommand.
